![Episode27.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1577205189528-RM3403IQWI6FS04KJN7T/Episode27.jpg)

The Source Wall is Broken! The Omega Titans are here! Brainiac needs the Justce League's help and Starro is back?! With Dark Nights Metal the guys at CBC decide to tackle the next mini event DC had to offer and that was Justice League: No Justice. With new threats on the horizon and new books on the docket can Scott Snyder really change the game....again?

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

